&lt;li&gt;Achieving and exceeding weekly/monthly metrics&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gain business knowledge through researching potential pain points, decision-making structures, and everyday business challenges of our target prospects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is an individual contributor role that reports to a Business Development Manager who values continuous improvement through weekly one-on-ones as well as providing you with the autonomy to allow you to steer your own success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Close alignment with Account Executives on pipeline organization and ongoing prospecting and nurture strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead prioritization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High volume prospecting and lead qualification through outbound phone calls, emails, and other channels&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regular team huddles to celebrate wins and share goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
